  = format: SOP-HG
  = format_profile: SOP-HG focal-point-layer

  + [N:focus:focal_point_object] is focal point object
    = focus_mode: right_hemisphere_focus
    = resolution_state: active
    = purpose: receive periphery draw and keep current attention thin enough to act
  + [N:subject:tracking_is_periphery] is tracking is the periphery layer
