  + [N:periphery:wide_dimensional_wander] is wide dimensional wander
  + [N:liminal:periphery_draws_focus] is periphery draw toward focal point
  + [N:term:right_hemisphere_focus] is context-led focus chase
  + [N:outside:focal_boundary] is related material not selected for current focus

